featureboard.Text_1: E lohe ʻia kou leo! ʻAe ʻoe e hoʻomohala mākou i kahi hiʻohiʻona a i ʻole bug? Kaomi i ke pihi e kākoʻo iā ia.
featureboard.Text_2: Makemake mākou e hoʻomohala i kahi hiʻohiʻona hou? E wehewehe i lalo.
featureboard.Text_3: I kēlā me kēia pule hoʻomaka mākou e hoʻomohala i ka hiʻohiʻona i noi ʻia e ke kaiāulu. ʻO nā kālā āpau i hāʻawi ʻia e hele i kēlā kumu, e ʻae iā mākou e hoʻomaikaʻi i ka app.
featureboard.Text_4: Hoʻohana ʻia nā kālā āpau i hāʻawi ʻia e kōkua i ka uku ʻana i kā mākou kumukūʻai hoʻomohala.
featureboard.Text_5: Loaʻa iā ʻoe kahi manaʻo no kahi hiʻohiʻona a i ʻole bugfix āu e makemake ai e hana mākou akā ʻaʻole ʻoe i ʻike i nā mea ʻē aʻe i hoʻohui hou? E wehewehe i lalo:
